Package: LINTCAS
Type: Package
Title: LINTUL CASSAVA crop growth simulation model
Version: 0.0-3
Date: 2026-01-03
Imports: deSolve
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Suggests: litedown
VignetteBuilder: litedown 
Author: Joy Adiele, Rob van den Beuken, Guillaume Ezui, Peter Leffelaar, Tom Schut
Maintainer: Robert Hijmans <r.hijmans@gmail.com>
Description: This package implements a LINTUL crop growth simulation model for cassava. It is a packaged version of the LINTUL_Cassava_NPK model R code available here https://models.pps.wur.nl/index.php/lintulcassavanpk (2024-10-2100). The packaging was done to facilitate the use of the model.
License: EUPL
